  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join us on Discord!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>Pick your weapon, your spell, your music, and you are ready to go.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DESTROY EVERYTHING</h2><br>Sword, grenades, teleport?<br>Choose your way to go, and blast your enemies in flow with the music!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1938850/extras/85b3711bf573b64f49c1c49822321326.poster.avif?t=1660905474\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1938850/extras/85b3711bf573b64f49c1c49822321326.webm?t=1660905474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1938850/extras/85b3711bf573b64f49c1c49822321326.mp4?t=1660905474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MUSICAL BULLET HELL</h2><br>Canon, lasers, arrows, explosive shapes and more!<br>Everything strikes to the beat! The higher the tempo, the higher the difficulty, use your dash to get away!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1938850/extras/8a2ae9b901a484579894691ee6a09425.poster.avif?t=1660905474\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1938850/extras/8a2ae9b901a484579894691ee6a09425.webm?t=1660905474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1938850/extras/8a2ae9b901a484579894691ee6a09425.mp4?t=1660905474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GO THROUGH ALL ROOMS</h2><br>You will have to face many rooms full of enemies. Each one with its own layout and bullet hell pattern.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BECOME STRONGER</h2><br>Want more weapon damage? More health? More dashes? Pick perks to complete your build!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNLOCK EVERYTHING</h2><br>Get new weapons, new spells, new soundtracks, and unlock trophies you can expose above your head!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE GAME IS TOO EASY?</h2><br>Add spikes, reduce your sight, add some glitching TV filter, face as many challenges as you can!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1938850/extras/b893e71cc4fe71c34d258d6f6c1440f8.poster.avif?t=1660905474\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1938850/extras/b893e71cc4fe71c34d258d6f6c1440f8.webm?t=1660905474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1938850/extras/b893e71cc4fe71c34d258d6f6c1440f8.mp4?t=1660905474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GET THE CROWN</h2><br>Compete with other players in a daily leaderboard with unique rewards!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Game feel tuned with care.<br></li><li> A catchy original soundtrack by the composer of Neon Beats.<br></li><li> Many weapons and spells with unique mechanics.<br></li><li> Challenges to increase the difficulty.<br></li><li> More than 64 trophies to unlock.<br></li><li> A leaderboard which resets every day.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Pick your weapon, your spell, your music, and you are ready to go.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DESTROY EVERYTHING</h2><br>Sword, grenades, teleport?<br>Choose your way to go, and blast your enemies in flow with the music!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1938850/extras/85b3711bf573b64f49c1c49822321326.poster.avif?t=1660905474\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1938850/extras/85b3711bf573b64f49c1c49822321326.webm?t=1660905474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1938850/extras/85b3711bf573b64f49c1c49822321326.mp4?t=1660905474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MUSICAL BULLET HELL</h2><br>Canon, lasers, arrows, explosive shapes and more!<br>Everything strikes to the beat! The higher the tempo, the higher the difficulty, use your dash to get away!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1938850/extras/8a2ae9b901a484579894691ee6a09425.poster.avif?t=1660905474\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1938850/extras/8a2ae9b901a484579894691ee6a09425.webm?t=1660905474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1938850/extras/8a2ae9b901a484579894691ee6a09425.mp4?t=1660905474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GO THROUGH ALL ROOMS</h2><br>You will have to face many rooms full of enemies. Each one with its own layout and bullet hell pattern.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BECOME STRONGER</h2><br>Want more weapon damage? More health? More dashes? Pick perks to complete your build!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNLOCK EVERYTHING</h2><br>Get new weapons, new spells, new soundtracks, and unlock trophies you can expose above your head!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE GAME IS TOO EASY?</h2><br>Add spikes, reduce your sight, add some glitching TV filter, face as many challenges as you can!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1938850/extras/b893e71cc4fe71c34d258d6f6c1440f8.poster.avif?t=1660905474\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1938850/extras/b893e71cc4fe71c34d258d6f6c1440f8.webm?t=1660905474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1938850/extras/b893e71cc4fe71c34d258d6f6c1440f8.mp4?t=1660905474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GET THE CROWN</h2><br>Compete with other players in a daily leaderboard with unique rewards!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Game feel tuned with care.<br></li><li> A catchy original soundtrack by the composer of Neon Beats.<br></li><li> Many weapons and spells with unique mechanics.<br></li><li> Challenges to increase the difficulty.<br></li><li> More than 64 trophies to unlock.<br></li><li> A leaderboard which resets every day.</li></ul>",
